{
  "stem": "3638.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have no idea, but I know one thing, that I knew him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All I-- when I saw him, I said good morning and good evening, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody was important except him, but I knew a lot of people who were there working on the factory.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was the only one who worked in the office.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pemper.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pemper was in, in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wasn't in Emalia from the beginning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He came after, when the Schindler list was made.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pemper, I know from before the war, because Pemper's brother used to go with me to school, to the Polish school, and he could not-- he was very bad in geography.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I was sitting in the first row, the teacher called him, show me where France is.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he looked up in, in where Scandinavia is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I, I said to him, down, down, down, and [LAUGHS] eventually he caught France.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He saw on there written, France, and he caught it, and we used to be good friends, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And through that, he put a good word to his brother when the list was made in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mietek.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mietek.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know, was it Mietek, or-- I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of them was [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Ignatz ?] Pemper, one was Mietek Pemper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because when, when I was in Plaszow, when I knew that it was going to-- they need 1,000 people for the, for the list.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, put a good word for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said that I should make sure that I'd been on list.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I didn't even rely on him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went direct to his brother, and he knew me, too, and he said to me, I will be on the list.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
